    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>相片大师 2025 极致版</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用 AI 工具进行影像优化，实现细致的画质调整与流畅的使用体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI 图片画质修復</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管是想要修復老照片还是单纯提升照片画质，都可以透过这项功能一次达到照片模糊修復、提高解析度、去噪点和除雾等效果，并轻松修復脸部细节，使图片更清晰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras/bb65d2d6d81fa1b7b685712d98416e3e.avif?t=1754573653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras_big/bb65d2d6d81fa1b7b685712d98416e3e.avif?t=1754573653 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI 物件移除</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强大的 AI 功能可自动辨别图像中的物件，只需一键即可移除不需要的元素；或者您也可以简单地涂画线条、圆圈或方框覆盖或围绕想移除的物件，AI 将准确地勾勒出轮廓，并可快速、精确地移除。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras/8647141ec7233cca4c676d1fdfc8d55c.avif?t=1754573653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras_big/8647141ec7233cca4c676d1fdfc8d55c.avif?t=1754573653 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >图片去背和换背景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速精准地帮图片去背，并可编辑背景颜色、模糊程度或上传自己的图片作为背景。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras/84f470abb63c08ae6a0e377d366252d9.avif?t=1754573653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras_big/84f470abb63c08ae6a0e377d366252d9.avif?t=1754573653 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一键脸部修饰</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一键立即套用多种人像修饰设定，快速打造无暇美颜。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras/4b82306bcb41564b4be758af93708663.avif?t=1754573653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras_big/4b82306bcb41564b4be758af93708663.avif?t=1754573653 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI 脸部去模糊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将脸部去模糊的同时保持背景模糊，在人像照等相片中创造自然的焦点效果。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras/461d4816ef3a3d2d26586ef4bdd37267.avif?t=1754573653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras_big/461d4816ef3a3d2d26586ef4bdd37267.avif?t=1754573653 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >脸部工具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >细腻地修饰和调整您的脸部，可以迅速调整脸型、美白牙齿、去除皱纹和油光等脸部瑕疵，或甚至细修额头、下巴和脸颊等细节。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras/a2d616854f6e8994fb79e1eba9809ab0.avif?t=1754573653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras_big/a2d616854f6e8994fb79e1eba9809ab0.avif?t=1754573653 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自动色调修饰</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动为您调整照片的曝光和对比等设定，同时确保相片细节被完整保留，完美呈现出最合适的色调。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras/2e56308edb13313018f945b3115dc8da.avif?t=1754573653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras_big/2e56308edb13313018f945b3115dc8da.avif?t=1754573653 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI 风格特效</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AI 风格转换特效，可以透过强大的 AI 技术，将您的照片转变成全新风格，像是：抽象画、素描、油画或浮世绘等。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras/a194442dace60734e3bce74ae55b1310.avif?t=1754573653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras_big/a194442dace60734e3bce74ae55b1310.avif?t=1754573653 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >模煳工具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >套用可客製调整的模煳效果到您的照片上，可选择圆形、线性或笔刷模煳工具，也能调整模煳类型和模煳程度。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras/979bd00d1ccd8dd1aa18f316063e95f9.avif?t=1754573653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras_big/979bd00d1ccd8dd1aa18f316063e95f9.avif?t=1754573653 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >图层遮色片</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可透过图层遮色片分层调整部分相片内容，让照片更独具风格。例如，只保留照片主题色彩，将背景改成黑白等。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras/d9e5878824fc39f71ae1d527b5c54777.avif?t=1754573653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146030/extras_big/d9e5878824fc39f71ae1d527b5c54777.avif?t=1754573653 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
